%% Diagram: High Level Architecture
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart TB
    CLIENTS["Clients\nMobile · Desktop · Web · Smart Speakers"]
    GW["API Gateway\nauth + routing"]
    CORE["Core Services\nPlayback · Catalog · Playlist · Search · Recommendation"]
    DATA["Data Layer\nCassandra · Postgres · Bigtable · Cache"]
    CDN["Multi-CDN\nAkamai · Fastly · AWS"]
    ORIGIN[("GCS Audio Origin")]
    EVENTS["Event Pipeline\nPub/Sub → Dataflow → BigQuery"]

    CLIENTS --> GW --> CORE --> DATA
    CORE --> CDN --> ORIGIN
    GW --> EVENTS
